==Description==
'''Valentin''' is a [[Franco]] Miner, one of the many inhabitants on the [[Island of the Francos]]. Just like all the other Francos on the island, Valentin is searching for their lost [[Francos Fragment|Key Fragment]]. He uses a dowsing pendulum to find it.

==Role in Twinsen's adventure==
Valentin gave [[Twinsen]] a clue, that the fragment might be buried near the gas.

